{"tid":2277281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE歌曲成反川普主題曲？真相曝光！女神卡卡是關鍵","createTime":"2020-11-08T10:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T00:39:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"faf79e7a654cb2b56ec66e6dc48b6eba4109e767","tid":2277281,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選在拜登宣布當選後告了一個段落，網路上也開始出現許多明星祝賀的影片，但近日就有人發現從本月6日開始，在twice官方YouTube頻道內《Feel Special》的MV中，有數以萬計的美國人前來留言，也讓這首歌悄悄成為美國總統候選人拜登的代表歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n而其中《Feel Special》下方的留言內容包括「即使我不是美國人，也要奉勸大家不可以投給川普」、「川普絕對不能再連任」等等反對川普的言論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/08/2869749-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F08%2F2869749-PH.jpg&h=8a7b174e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲女神Lady Gaga在喬治亞州的開票結果拜登反敗爲勝後，在舞台上開心的隨著《Feel special》起舞。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n但其實會有這樣的狀況是因為，女神Lady Gaga在日前喬治亞州的開票結果拜登反敗爲勝後，在舞台上開心的隨著《Feel special》起舞，掀起美國民眾熱烈的討論，更讓《Feel special》瞬間成爲反對川普的主題曲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/itmedahyun/status/1325059697280380928?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1325059697280380928%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F844657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fitmedahyun%2Fstatus%2F1325059697280380928%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1325059697280380928%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.setn.com%252Fnews%252F844657&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq70x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=7dc20cb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fitmedahyun%2Fstatus%2F1325059697280380928%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1325059697280380928%257Ctwgr%255Eshare_3%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.setn.com%252Fnews%252F844657&h=fd41d66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/itmedahyun/status/1325059697280380928?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1325059697280380928%7Ctwgr%5Eshare_3&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.setn.com%2Fnews%2F844657</a>"},{"pid":"4bfb64717c2a735210b2e5335d14b823221aeddc","tid":2277281,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:00:49.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c04b77cc66578c0dd7cc4e0efba031a83c67b7b","tid":2277281,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾twice"},{"pid":"56ff2ec88f501f38ee61c68c4451dd6b856d57d6","tid":2277281,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"dye你老母迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222eb304a4ffcc43f00a44cd59a4175142628e06","tid":2277281,"uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，要我係T寶同侵仔兩邊取捨<br />\n好絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n囡死囡還在，我揀侵，反T寶"},{"pid":"2747a306c4a7dc3cd64fada2e79c2644e1e4d9a9","tid":2277281,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c04b77cc66578c0dd7cc4e0efba031a83c67b7b","tid":2277281,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾twice"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"twice是無菇的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ae1ce6ced1128ead66cf72359d5d1492c9c2b5","tid":2277281,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"222eb304a4ffcc43f00a44cd59a4175142628e06","tid":2277281,"uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，要我係T寶同侵仔兩邊取捨<br />\n好絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n囡死囡還在，我揀侵，反T寶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"twice是無菇俾人擺上抬的 即係twice支持侵<img src=